<section xml:id="_md_public_2glpi_2vendor_2guzzlehttp_2promises_2_c_h_a_n_g_e_l_o_g_1autotoc_md6085">
<title><title>1.1.0 - 2016-03-07</title></title>
<section xml:id="_md_public_2glpi_2vendor_2guzzlehttp_2promises_2_c_h_a_n_g_e_l_o_g_1autotoc_md6086">
<title><title>Changed</title></title>

<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<para><link linkend="_class_update">Update</link> EachPromise to prevent recurring on a iterator when advancing, as this could trigger fatal generator errors.</para>
</listitem><listitem>
<para><link linkend="_class_update">Update</link> Promise to allow recursive waiting without unwrapping exceptions.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</section>
</section>
<section xml:id="_md_public_2glpi_2vendor_2guzzlehttp_2promises_2_c_h_a_n_g_e_l_o_g_1autotoc_md6087">
<title><title>1.0.3 - 2015-10-15</title></title>
<section xml:id="_md_public_2glpi_2vendor_2guzzlehttp_2promises_2_c_h_a_n_g_e_l_o_g_1autotoc_md6088">
<title><title>Changed</title></title>

<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<para><link linkend="_class_update">Update</link> EachPromise to immediately resolve when the underlying promise iterator is empty. Previously, such a promise would throw an exception when its <computeroutput>wait</computeroutput> function was called.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</section>
</section>
