<section xml:id="_md_public_2glpi_2vendor_2guzzlehttp_2promises_2_c_h_a_n_g_e_l_o_g_1autotoc_md6091">
<title><title>1.0.1 - 2015-06-24</title></title>
<section xml:id="_md_public_2glpi_2vendor_2guzzlehttp_2promises_2_c_h_a_n_g_e_l_o_g_1autotoc_md6092">
<title><title>Changed</title></title>

<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<para>Updating EachPromise to call next on the underlying promise iterator as late as possible to ensure that generators that generate new requests based on callbacks are not iterated until after callbacks are invoked.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</section>
</section>
